                <note>The canons are ascribed to <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/575">John
                    of <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/66">Damascus</placeName>
                  </persName>,
                  <foreign xml:lang="syr-x-syrm">ܩܫܝܫܐ</foreign> (or <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܘܚܢܢ</foreign>) <foreign xml:lang="syr-x-syrm">ܐܒܐ ܝܘܢܝ ܕܪܡܣܘܩܝܐ ܒܪ ܡܢܨܘܪ</foreign>
